JOHANNESBURG Stands at the 22nd St John s College Easter Rugby Festival were packed to the rafters throughout the three-day festival.Day three ended on Monday with St John s College (Harare) squaring up to Hilton College in the first game. Hosts St John s played debutantes Eye of the Tiger, beating them 57 10.In the final showdown of the festival, the game between Afrikaanse Ho r Seunskool (Affies) and the top ranked school in South Africa, Paarl Boys High, got off to a flying start.Paarl defeated Affies by 14 points to 10. eNCA